103
00:06:11.184 --> 00:06:13.784
confusion. So on this slide, we have some

104
00:06:14.644 --> 00:06:18.524
examples of things that we've seen in analyst reports from

105
00:06:18.564 --> 00:06:22.484
Wall Street on a website that allows people to line

