159
00:09:21.734 --> 00:09:25.364
across industry, academia, patients, clinicians

160
00:09:25.444 --> 00:09:29.324
to really understand what it is that they're being served

161
00:09:29.384 --> 00:09:32.604
up and how they can interpret it. So we've come up with this framework,

162
00:09:33.764 --> 00:09:37.324
which is at the end of the day, sort of how you fill out your

163
00:09:37.364 --> 00:09:40.524
two-by-two table, which you have to do if you're doing a clinical validation study.

164
00:09:40.584 --> 00:09:43.644
But what are the things that we also have to understand about the data that went

165
00:09:43.744 --> 00:09:47.124
into that two-by-two table in order to really have the right context for

