178
00:10:25.324 --> 00:10:29.304
So that's whether it's a single cancer, many cancers, all cancers.

179
00:10:30.044 --> 00:10:33.244
You really have to understand that in order to interpret this two-by-two table.

180
00:10:34.444 --> 00:10:36.954
You have to define what the clinical ground truth is.

181
00:10:37.004 --> 00:10:40.914
How do you know that the people in a clinical validation study had or did not have

182
00:10:40.944 --> 00:10:44.644
cancer? And we had, as Tina said, a session about that at AACR

