00:19:01.402 --> 00:19:05.352
and they tend to be correlated with a larger, more advanced,

320
00:19:05.372 --> 00:19:09.212
and more aggressive tumor. And given the reign of sojourn times, which

321
00:19:09.232 --> 00:19:12.672
we don't understand particularly well, but you can imagine with a large number of

322
00:19:12.732 --> 00:19:16.372
cancers, they're going to have different detectable preclinical phases.

323
00:19:17.372 --> 00:19:21.292
The lower detection of circulating markers for earlier stage cancers

