00:21:38.612 --> 00:21:42.052
for the aggregate mix of tumors, and for the individual cancers.

364
00:21:42.672 --> 00:21:46.452
This is a very useful measure of sensitivity, as is how your

365
00:21:46.472 --> 00:21:49.972
test is performing with the predictability of the

366
00:21:50.172 --> 00:21:53.662
first signal for tumor of origin and the second, and

367
00:21:54.072 --> 00:21:54.932
the two combined.

