00:22:00.112 --> 00:22:02.292
relatively well, as you can see from these numbers here.

370
00:22:04.072 --> 00:22:07.841
Now, an MCED test with moderate aggregate sensitivity will

371
00:22:07.952 --> 00:22:11.522
have a larger public health impact than a higher sensitivity single

